{"tid":1373494,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"葉虎單野打唔入","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T02:59:06.000Z","uid":291601,"like":4,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c00cf84d981f984bf97a201b2a3b742274e13680","tid":1373494,"uid":291601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:36:10.000Z","msg":"P牌新仔小分析<br />\n<br />\n南邊圍停車場，市民打爛黑幫私家車，因為見到有藤條。<br />\n打散咗，見到大量武器，但重點係解放軍帽，同埋蘋果影到的電費單，仲有一張告票，一本南亞文數簿。<br />\n<br />\n私家車車主已經證實咗係南亞人<br />\n解放軍帽係舊款<br />\n電費單係南邊圍入面，叫YIP FOO，蘋果話業權持有幾代，應該唔係中聯辦嗰個<br />\n告票好似唔關事<br />\n數簿希望有人拎番去翻譯<br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦！車入面有大量武器，好大機會係黑社會，南亞仔，傻更更唔記得收埋架車，幫大哥YIP FOO交電費。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係頂舊款軍帽點解釋！？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3ee114d6ea806728c3cf4b217e431ab89bf1a7f8","tid":1373494,"uid":46966,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ON9點解係我地解 有証據<br />\n條友會出黎解嫁啦 你解乜春"},{"pid":"56074c17c3aed8cfbeb2fd4673d59ca1902998fd","tid":1373494,"uid":291601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ee114d6ea806728c3cf4b217e431ab89bf1a7f8","tid":1373494,"uid":46966,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />ON9點解係我地解 有証據<br />\n條友會出黎解嫁啦 你解乜春"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"因為根本唔會有人出黎解"},{"pid":"8bf5cf90a4e5041f69bb08e44f1b0586647efea9","tid":1373494,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:09:43.000Z","msg":"官官相衞<br />\n五黑勾結<br />\n指鹿為馬<br />\n滿口謊言<br />\n埋沒良心<br />\n必遭天譴<br />\n若然未報<br />\n時辰未到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警、黑鄉、黑官、黑鐵、黑幫<br />\n清算日時，全員